verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Divine anointing dwells within me,
And it teaches me all things;
It ever leads me in the Lord to live
And to me His presence brings.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}It is the moving of the Spirit,
Precious as the ointment pure;
It’s based upon the sprinkling of the blood,
And it ever shall endure.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}It’s by this inner life anointing
I in fellowship may move;
In God, the light of truth, I’m walking,
And the love of grace I prove.{/lang-eng}
